ssh配置并开启
1. vi /etc/ssh/sshd_config
+ 密码验证
PermitRootLogin yes
PasswordAuthentication yes
+ 秘钥对验证
RSAAuthentication yes
PubkeyAuthentication yes
AuthorizedKeysFile .ssh/authorized_keys
(需要在.ssh/authorized_keys加入公钥)
2. 启动ssh  /etc/init.d/ssh start
查看ssh服务状态 /etc/init.d/ssh status

ssh-keygen的使用
ssh-keygen -t rsa -C "youremail@email.com" -f ~/.ssh/second
touch ~/.ssh/config
chmod 600 ~/.ssh/config

git中ssh
1. ssh -vT git@github.com
2. ssh -i ~/.ssh/github_rsa -T git@github.com
3. git clone github-user1:user1/project.git 
(github-user1指的是在config文件配置中Host对应的名称)
相当于git clone git@github.com:HudsonWu/linuxStudying.git
